data.title: Disney Sing Your Heart Out!
data.meta_description: Disney Sing Your Heart Out! is a compilation box-set that includes 3 albums featuring Disney songs. It was released on October 19, 2018 by Walt Disney Records.
data.text:
Disney Sing Your Heart Out! is a compilation box-set that includes 3 albums featuring Disney songs. It was released on October 19, 2018 by Walt Disney Records.
